seeds.title: Fjallraven Foldsack No. 1 Backpack
seeds.tagline: Simple functional backpack in G-1000 HeavyDuty Eco
seeds.description: Unembellished backpack with a simple and functional design where the top can be folded down and attached to the front with textile straps and metal buckles. Made from extra strong and durable G-1000 HeavyDuty Eco. The large main compartment can be accessed through the turned down top, and it has an inner pocket with padding at the bottom for a laptop (15 inch).

seeds.title: Tortuga Prelude Travel Backpack
seeds.tagline: The fully-featured carry on for organized travelers
seeds.description: If you’re going to backpack around the world, you need a travel backpack that’s carry-on-sized, organized, and comfortable to carry.

seeds.title: Peak Design Travel Backpack 45L
seeds.tagline: A versatile, durable, and beautiful carry-on travel backpack driven by a simple truth: no two trips are the same.
seeds.description: Features top, side, front and rear access via intuitively placed weatherproof zips. Meets international carry-on size requirements, but expands to be a 45L gear-hauler and collapses to be a 35L day bag, making it unmatched for 1-bag travel. Tons of internal and external pockets, plus a main cavity that’s divisible via a zippered mesh sleeve.

seeds.title: Aer Travel Pack 2
seeds.tagline: Featured in Wirecutter's "The Best Carry-On Travel Backpacks"
seeds.description: The Travel Pack 2 is a versatile carry-on backpack designed for traveling smart. Breeze through security checkpoints, skip the baggage carousel and quickly access your travel essentials on the go.

seeds.title: Atlas Supply Minimalist - Sand
seeds.tagline: The Minimalist is the perfect backpack for anyone who wears multiple hats, but doesn’t want to wear multiple bags.
seeds.description: The separate laptop section holds up to a 15″ laptop with padded siding & bottom for extra protection. This is also a great section for books, papers and folders.

seeds.title: REI Co-op Ruckpack 18 Recycled Daypack
seeds.tagline: If you plan to see it all in a day—this is the travel pack for you. The 18-liter REI Co-op Ruckpack is strong, comfy and impeccably organized.
seeds.description: Now made with rugged, recycled ripstop nylon that withstands whatever the road throws your way. Lightly padded shoulder straps provide carrying comfort; sternum strap gives extra stability when you're running to a departure gate.

seeds.title: Cotopaxi Allpa 35L Travel Pack
seeds.tagline: Carry-on-compatible and ultra hardy, this is our best-selling adventure travel pack.
seeds.description: With thousands of customers’ feedback in mind, we created the second-generation Allpa 35L Travel Pack: a lighter and more durable version of our best-selling backpack system built for all types of exploration. This pack is perfectly sized for carry-on convenience, loaded with well-designed features, and tough enough to handle years of use.

seeds.title: NOMATIC 40L Travel Bag
seeds.tagline: The NOMATIC 40L Travel Bag is the perfect travel bag for those 3-7 day trips.
seeds.description: There are multiple compartments for shoes, clothes, tech, and even a water bottle pocket to help you keep you gear organized as you travel. With over 20 features, this is the perfect travel bag for a weekend getaway or an extended vacation.

seeds.title: WANDRD HEXAD Access Duffel Backpack
seeds.tagline: Built for 3-5 day trips, this bag is weather-resistant, durable, and extremely functional.
seeds.description: The HEXAD Access Duffel Backpack is a carry-on sized backpack/duffel hybrid that features a clamshell opening and is the perfect travel bag, whether you're a photographer or not.
